#  To execute do the following:

#  get all the components in a folder, the said components are:

#  arithematic.cpp  Makefile       tcpClient.h        tcpServer.h      udpClient.cpp  udpServer.h
#  arithematic.h    README         tcpclientMain.cpp  tserverMain.cpp  udpClient.h    userverMain.cpp
#  headers.h        tcpClient.cpp  tcpServer.cpp      uclientMain.cpp  udpServer.cpp


#  go to terminal in th above directory and give command:
make

#  to run server UDP Server
./userver

#to run UDP client... the number1 = num1, operator = op and number2 = num2 
./uclient num1 op num2


#  to run server TCP Server
./tserver

#to run TCP client... the number1 = num1, operator = op and number2 = num2 
./tclient num1 op num2

